{
  "stem": "15028.1",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, well, I-- well, most of the people in my town belonged to, one way or the other, to Hasidic or to some kind of rabbi-- a rabbi, not some kind.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I would say a rabbi.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If it was a [NON-ENGLISH] or the-- or [NON-ENGLISH], or [NON-ENGLISH], every-- somehow, the majority belonged to, one way or another, to the-- to a rabbi, to a [NON-ENGLISH] rabbi.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, but I have my grand-grandfather was a [NON-ENGLISH] in-- in the area.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he lived in Moisei.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't practice over here, but he was a [NON-ENGLISH], was a Talmud-- a rabbi, and he wrote [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Matter of fact, I own-- he wrote five ciphers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I own some of them, but [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And lately, we found an-- he-- he went away to-- to Palestine, in that time, in the late 1800s, to die in-- in Israel.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he died in Tsefat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they found some of his writings in Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we went ahead, and we translated it in-- in Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had a lot of-- quite a few [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the cipher that's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This we pre-printed it, printed 1,000 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] books, [NON-ENGLISH], and-- [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not for profit-making, but we printed them for-- well, I-- we consider, my cousins in Israel consider, it's more like a-- [NON-ENGLISH], all about being.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everything what you put them out or make a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it's very well expressed and written.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His comments are terrific.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We printed it, not for profit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a feeling that we had money, a tzedakah fund that we established through the family in Tel Aviv.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that money is-- we lend it to people in need, but interest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that money is put back.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
